AUTHORITATIVE DATA POLICY
- This document is the sole authoritative source for wishlist entries, tracker rules, section rules, pricing rules, platform restrictions, edition preferences, matching rules, and notification rules.
- Every rule, note, field, and listed item in this document is operative unless the document explicitly states otherwise.
- The current contents of this document take precedence over previous versions, prior conversations, memory, assumptions, and external interpretations.
- Previous versions or remembered copies must never be used to restore removed items, rules, or preferences.
- A monitoring system must retrieve and interpret the current document before every scan.
- If this document cannot be retrieved, is incomplete or malformed, or uses an unsupported schema, the monitoring system must stop rather than guess or perform a partial scan.

GLOBAL TRACKER RULES
- Search only items explicitly listed in this file.
- Bundles, collections, remasters, and complete editions may be reported when they include a listed item.
- Every reported opportunity must include a direct purchase/listing link when available.
- Include seller/store, current price, shipping, taxes when known, timestamp, condition/edition, and market context.
- Use recent sold prices, normal market value, and historical lows when available.
- Do not repeat an unchanged listing unless price, availability, seller, condition, or urgency materially changes.
- Alert ratings: ⭐ Buy Now; 🚨 Rare Listing; 🟣 Collector Deal; 🔵 Great Deal; 🟢 Good Deal; 🆕 New Release/Preorder; 🔄 Restock.

