SECTION RULES
- All physical games must be US-region versions.
- Physical = Physical only.
- Digital = Digital only.
- Physical or Digital = Either format is acceptable; compare eligible stores and report the cheapest qualifying option.
- Physical-only game listings should be legitimate, good-condition CIB copies from reputable sellers.
- PlayStation Store: notify whenever a listed game drops below $10, even if it is not a historical low.
- eBay physical-only items: report abnormally low-priced active listings compared with typical market value.
- Exact title matching is required, except qualifying bundles/collections/remasters/complete editions containing a listed title.

